 7.3 级地震", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTc1ODgwNDA3ODQyNjM1MzY2NXITMTc1ODgwNDA3ODQyNjM1MzY2NXgA", "tag": "直播", "tag_bg_color": "GRD07A"}, {"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/org/pi-yao-qian-xian", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}